  "mainClass": "flex-1 flex bg-surface-container-low overflow-hidden min-h-0",
  "mainHtml": "<aside class=\"history-panel flex flex-col h-full min-h-0 bg-surface border-r border-outline-variant shrink-0\" id=\"historyPanel\">\n<div class=\"history-head-wrap p-4 border-b border-outline-variant\">\n<div class=\"history-head flex items-center justify-between gap-3\">\n<div class=\"history-brand flex items-center gap-3 min-w-0\">\n<div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary-container text-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[20px]\">history</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"history-copy min-w-0\">\n<p class=\"text-label-md font-bold text-on-surface\">对话历史</p>\n<p class=\"text-label-sm text-secondary truncate\">文字转模型任务记录</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<button class=\"p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-surface-container-low transition-colors shrink-0\" id=\"historyToggle\" type=\"button\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">chevron_left</span>\n</button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"history-search mt-4 relative\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-[18px] text-on-surface-variant\">search</span>\n<input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low py-2 pl-10 pr-3 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" placeholder=\"搜索历史任务\" type=\"text\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"history-list flex-1 overflow-y-auto p-4 space-y-3 chat-scroll\">\n<button class=\"history-item is-current w-full rounded-2xl border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5 p-3 text-left transition-colors hover:bg-primary/10\" title=\"发动机支架需求任务\" type=\"button\">\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n<div class=\"history-item-icon mt-0.5 w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-primary text-on-primary flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">description</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"history-item-copy min-w-0\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-2\">\n<span class=\"text-body-sm font-bold text-on-surface truncate\">发动机支架需求</span>\n<span class=\"text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant shrink-0\">10:42</span>\n</div>\n<p class=\"mt-1 text-[11px] text-on-surface-variant line-clamp-2\">V6 总成支架，轻量化、45kg 静载、安全系数 2.0，当前进入参数确认阶段。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</button>\n<button class=\"history-item w-full rounded-2xl border border-transparent bg-surface-container-low p-3 text-left transition-colors hover:border-outline-variant hover:bg-surface-container\" title=\"泵体外壳优化任务\" type=\"button\">\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n<div class=\"history-item-icon mt-0.5 w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-surface-container-high text-on-surface flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">deployed_code</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"history-item-copy min-w-0\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-2\">\n<span class=\"text-body-sm font-bold text-on-surface truncate\">泵体外壳优化</span>\n<span class=\"text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant shrink-0\">昨天</span>\n</div>\n<p class=\"mt-1 text-[11px] text-on-surface-variant line-clamp-2\">要求保留外形轮廓，内部筋位允许优化，适配 CNC 加工。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</button>\n<button class=\"history-item w-full rounded-2xl border border-transparent bg-surface-container-lowest p-3 text-left transition-colors hover:border-outline-variant hover:bg-surface-container-low\" title=\"机器人支臂结构任务\" type=\"button\">\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n<div class=\"history-item-icon mt-0.5 w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-surface-container text-on-surface flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">smart_toy</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"history-item-copy min-w-0\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between gap-2\">\n<span class=\"text-body-sm font-bold text-on-surface truncate\">机器人支臂结构</span>\n<span class=\"text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant shrink-0\">7月03日</span>\n</div>\n<p class=\"mt-1 text-[11px] text-on-surface-variant line-clamp-2\">文字需求已转人工复核，待补充装配关系和配合孔信息。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"history-footer p-4 border-t border-outline-variant\">\n<button class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-4 py-2 text-[12px] font-bold text-primary hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors\" type=\"button\">\n查看全部历史\n</button>\n</div>\n</aside><section class=\"flex-1 flex flex-col min-w-0 min-h-0 h-full p-6 relative\">\n<div class=\"relative flex-1 flex flex-col bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-outline-variant overflow-hidden min-h-0\">\n<div class=\"px-6 py-4 border-b border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest flex-shrink-0\">\n<div class=\"flex w-fit p-1 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl\">\n<a class=\"px-6 py-2 font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface transition-colors\" href=\"/ai/smart-quote\">智能报价</a>\n<a class=\"px-6 py-2 font-label-md text-label-md bg-surface-container-lowest text-primary font-bold shadow-sm rounded-lg\" href=\"/ai/text-to-3d\">文字转模型</a>\n<a class=\"px-6 py-2 font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface-variant hover:text-on-surface transition-colors\" href=\"/ai/image-to-3d\">图片转模型</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex-1 min-h-0 overflow-y-auto p-6 pb-56 space-y-8 chat-scroll\">\n<div class=\"flex flex-col items-end\">\n<div class=\"bg-primary text-on-primary p-4 rounded-2xl rounded-tr-none max-w-lg shadow-md\">\n<p class=\"text-body-sm\">请生成一个用于 V6 总成的轻量化铝合金发动机支架。需承受 45kg 静载，安全系数 2.0，并针对 CNC 铣削工艺优化。</p>\n</div>\n<span class=\"text-[10px] text-on-surface-variant mt-1 px-2\">10:42 AM</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"flex flex-col items-start\">\n<div class=\"flex gap-3 max-w-[calc(100%-2rem)]\">\n<div class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary-container flex items-center justify-center text-primary shrink-0\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\" style=\"font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;\">auto_awesome</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"space-y-4 min-w-0\">\n<div class=\"bg-surface-container-high p-4 rounded-2xl rounded-tl-none shadow-sm border border-outline-variant\">\n<p class=\"text-body-sm text-on-surface\">我已理解你的文字需求。为了避免 AI 直接生成后模型与制造条件不符，我会先逐项收集尺寸、公差、材料、工艺、装配和输出格式，再生成模型并同步右侧报价与下单信息。</p>\n<div class=\"mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2\">\n<button class=\"rounded-xl bg-primary px-4 py-2 text-[12px] font-bold text-on-primary hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity\" data-scroll-wizard=\"\" type=\"button\">开始参数采集</button>\n<button class=\"rounded-xl border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5 px-4 py-2 text-[12px] font-bold text-primary hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors\" data-human-support=\"\" type=\"button\">转人工协助</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden rounded-2xl border border-[#f6c47a] bg-[#fff7eb] p-4 shadow-sm\" id=\"humanSupportCard\">\n<div class=\"flex items-start gap-3\">\n<div class=\"mt-0.5 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-[#ffedd5] text-[#c2410c] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0\">\n<span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]\">support_agent</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"min-w-0\">\n<p class=\"text-body-sm font-bold text-on-surface\">已准备转人工复核服务</p>\n<p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant\">如果 AI 对文字需求理解不稳定、结构过于复杂或你希望由工程师先确认关键条件，可以直接转人工继续处理。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest shadow-sm overflow-hidden\">\n<div class=\"p-4 border-b border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low\">\n<div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<div>\n<p class=\"text-body-sm font-bold text-on-surface\">推荐文字描述示例</p>\n<p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant\">你可以像下面这样描述零件需求，AI 会更容易理解并快速进入参数采集。</p>\n</div>\n<span class=\"rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold text-primary\">示例</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"p-4 bg-surface-container-lowest\">\n<div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-surface-container-low p-4 text-[12px] text-on-surface leading-6\">\n请生成一个用于 V6 发动机总成的轻量化支架。整体尺寸约为 320 x 110 x 96 mm，材料优先考虑铝合金 6061-T6，工艺为五轴 CNC 加工。需承受 45kg 静载，安全系数 2.0，四个安装孔必须同轴，外轮廓尽量保持紧凑，内部结构允许优化减重。公差要求标准 ±0.05mm，输出 STEP 文件，首批 20 件，交期 10 天。\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rounded-2xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-lowest shadow-sm overflow-hidden\" id=\"parameterWizard\">\n<div class=\"px-5 py-4 border-b border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low\">\n<div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<div>\n<p class=\"text-body-sm font-bold text-on-surface\">模型生成参数采集</p>\n<p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant\">基于你的文字需求，系统会逐步收集制造参数，再开始生成模型。</p>\n</div>\n<span class=\"rounded-full bg-primary/10 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold text-primary\" id=\"stepCounter\">第 1 / 5 步</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2\">\n<button class=\"step-trigger is-active rounded-xl bg-surface-container px-3 py-2 text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant transition-colors\" data-step-trigger=\"0\" type=\"button\">1. 尺寸与精度</button>\n<button class=\"step-trigger rounded-xl bg-surface-container px-3 py-2 text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant transition-colors\" data-step-trigger=\"1\" type=\"button\">2. 材料与工艺</button>\n<button class=\"step-trigger rounded-xl bg-surface-container px-3 py-2 text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant transition-colors\" data-step-trigger=\"2\" type=\"button\">3. 输出与 AI</button>\n<button class=\"step-trigger rounded-xl bg-surface-container px-3 py-2 text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant transition-colors\" data-step-trigger=\"3\" type=\"button\">4. 制造约束</button>\n<button class=\"step-trigger rounded-xl bg-surface-container px-3 py-2 text-[12px] text-on-surface-variant transition-colors\" data-step-trigger=\"4\" type=\"button\">5. 补充与确认</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"p-5\">\n<div class=\"space-y-6\" data-step-panel=\"0\">\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">整体长度</span><input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" placeholder=\"例如 320\" type=\"number\" value=\"320\"/></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">整体宽度</span><input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" placeholder=\"例如 110\" type=\"number\" value=\"110\"/></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">整体高度</span><input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" placeholder=\"例如 96\" type=\"number\" value=\"96\"/></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">单位</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\"><option selected=\"\">mm</option><option>cm</option><option>inch</option></select></label>\n</div>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-4 py-3 text-body-sm text-on-surface\"><input checked=\"\" class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>是否允许 AI 估算缺失尺寸</label>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">公差 / 精度要求</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"toleranceSelect\"><option>标准 ±0.1 mm</option><option selected=\"\">标准 ±0.05 mm</option><option>精密 ±0.02 mm（需附 2D 图纸）</option><option>超精密 ±0.01 mm（需附 2D 图纸）</option></select></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">是否可加工</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\"><option selected=\"\">AI 预判可加工</option><option>明确可加工</option><option>暂不确定，需要人工判断</option></select></label>\n</div>\n<p class=\"rounded-xl bg-emerald-50 px-4 py-3 text-[12px] text-emerald-700\" id=\"toleranceHelper\">当前为标准精度，无需额外 2D 图纸。</p>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">最小壁厚</span><input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" placeholder=\"例如 3.0 mm\" type=\"text\" value=\"3.0 mm\"/></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">孔深</span><input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" placeholder=\"例如 28 mm\" type=\"text\" value=\"28 mm\"/></label>\n</div>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\">\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-4 py-3 text-[12px] text-on-surface\"><input checked=\"\" class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>AI 自动检测壁厚</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-3 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-4 py-3 text-[12px] text-on-surface\"><input checked=\"\" class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>允许优化壁厚</label>\n</div>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">配合关系</span><textarea class=\"min-h-[84px] w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" placeholder=\"例如：四个孔必须同轴，需与轴承外圈配合\">四个安装孔必须同轴，需与轴承外圈配合。</textarea></label>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">零件名称</span><input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"partNameInput\" type=\"text\" value=\"发动机支架\"/></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">零件用途</span><input class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"text\" value=\"发动机总成安装与承载\"/></label>\n<label class=\"block col-span-2\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">所属行业</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\"><option selected=\"\">汽车零部件</option><option>通用机械</option><option>机器人</option><option>医疗器械</option><option>消费电子</option><option>航空航天</option><option>其他</option></select></label>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden space-y-6\" data-step-panel=\"1\">\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\">\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">材料</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"materialSelect\"><option>铝合金 7075-T6</option><option selected=\"\">铝合金 6061-T6</option><option>不锈钢 304</option><option>不锈钢 316L</option><option>ABS 塑料</option><option>PC 聚碳酸酯</option><option>PEEK</option><option>其他</option><option>AI 推荐材料</option></select></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">加工方式 / 制造工艺</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"processSelect\"><option>CNC加工</option><option>钣金</option><option>3D打印</option><option>注塑</option><option>铸造</option><option>压铸</option><option>激光切割</option><option>车削</option><option>铣削</option><option selected=\"\">五轴加工</option><option>AI自动推荐基础</option></select></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">表面处理</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"surfaceSelect\"><option>无需处理</option><option>喷砂</option><option selected=\"\">阳极氧化</option><option>发黑</option><option>喷漆</option><option>拉丝</option><option>抛光</option><option>电镀</option><option>镀锌</option><option>镀镍</option><option>喷粉</option><option>AI推荐</option></select></label>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">AI 优化结构</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"structureSelect\"><option>不允许修改</option><option>允许优化</option><option selected=\"\">最大程度保证可加工性</option><option>最大程度保证文字描述一致</option></select></label>\n</div>\n<label class=\"block\"><span class=\"mb-2 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">生成目标</span><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2 text-body-sm focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary\" id=\"goalSelect\"><option>外观一致</option><option selected=\"\">可加工优先</option><option>成本最低</option><option>强度最高</option><option>重量最轻</option><option>AI自动平衡</option></select></label>\n<div>\n<span class=\"mb-3 block text-[12px] font-medium text-on-surface-variant\">孔与螺纹</span>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 text-[12px]\">\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input checked=\"\" class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>圆孔</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input checked=\"\" class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>螺纹孔</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>沉头孔</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>沉孔</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input checked=\"\" class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>定位孔</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>键槽</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input checked=\"\" class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>倒角</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input checked=\"\" class=\"h-4 w-4 rounded border-outline text-primary focus:ring-primary\" type=\"checkbox\"/>圆角</label>\n<label class=\"flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-outline-variant bg-surface-container-low px-3 py-2\"><input c